messages.content: Nalaiki kalaila volleyball play panna vaa
Ivanlu guest ah Vida maatanlu la
Abi ta solli santhos ah vara sollu
Entha team potalum win pana paruka
Ellarum parunka epti la play pananumnu athuvae kanum nxt odambu support pananu
Namaku edhum chinna team ah poduvaanlaaa
Pro kabbadi paru avanukale mari play pana thana varum
Avan meloor la play panum bodhe varala la
Santhosh ah ball ah kubta solu
King oda chinna payan dhN oruthan vaaran
King vandha erukalai pettila oruthana kammi pannalaam
Edhu mukkiyam diffence ah ride ah
Jan 14 morning Namma grnd ku vandhuruvaanlu
Ajan ah la kutuka ajish apti sina pasankalaium
Avanlu oorum South Athichaperi dhan la
Night solutha kata avan exam la iruka
And Jan 14 evlo periya work irundhalum adha thoora potutu paaka vandhuru
Naanga karisal la 2nd prize so bigg nu nenachi bigg team kooda potrukanlu
Adhu enga team poodhathan kudiyirupu kooda
Varavanuka nama uru pasanka mari play pana matanuka
Fixtures la erukalavetti nu iruku paaru
Apo ketu sollu apadi poda koodadhunu sonna Athichaperi nu entry kuduthuru
Athan school name na problem irukathu
Nee scl name serka vachalum okk dhan
2 guest player ku pasa maatenu sonnala adha sonnen
Scl team entry undaa nu kelu
Apadilaam onnum panna maatom nee pannama irundhaa sari dhaan bro ð
Namma oor pasanga vandha naanga edhukula summa sutha porom
Illana amir jamal school team nu poduka
Varuva but problem eathum pana kudathu idyankulam karan kuda santhu
Ee entry evlo nu fixtures ketu enaku sent pannu
Team ready panuka 3 days train agum
John ta ketadhuku King varalanu sollitaan
Naa abi John jeb neduvilai Akash erukalapatti aslin jerlin
Nee add panna sollu okk yaa la
I think fixtures la irukura erukalavetti Namma nu nenaiken
Namma team la koncham guest potaa nee un frnd ta pasipiyaa la
Fixtures la Namma name illa la
Ama na eara follow panurano avankala la matum tha pana mudium
Un story ku ennaala reply panna mudiyala
Na varra team kutitu varan pakalam
